name: aloop
description:
I truly like loops. There’s just something about them that is electrifying. This particular looping gif features green circles that emanate from the center of the field. They just keep on generating and it never ends. This was rendered with help from an NEC PC-88VA (a favorite graphics device of mine because of its endearing qualities). Moves at 30 frames per second.
